Dining room opens to the kitchen with stainless steel appliances, stove top, double ovens, lots of counter-space, pantry, and big laundry closet & window. Both bedrooms are off a central hall with linen closets and gorgeous newly remodeled baths. The master's en suite bath has a cute port-hole window, an oversized tile shower & a pretty new vanity with lights. The large full bath, off the central hall, doubles as a powder room & has a skylight, shower/tub combo, luxurious vanity & lighting. A single pane door leads from the family room to the private grassy & landscaped backyard with bistro lights for added atmosphere, evening dining & intimate gatherings. The Garage has been remodeled for use as a in- home office with finished walls & floors, outlets, windows & a glass door to let in more natural light.
